ients tell us – time and again our proprietary technology provides state of the art functionality to provide a level of support for front middle and back office functions that is more usually associated with investment bankstfg complete can be deployed as a hosted solution clients can log in from any internet desktop in the world this enables the software to be deployed quickly and efficiently to new clients average time for new installations is  months we use our skill and expertise to manage the software including regular new releases and bug fixes so that clients can concentrate on managing their fund and maximising returns tfg differentiates itself on giving outstanding service new clients are given direct access to the development team for the duration of the onboarding process and thereafter we work hard with clients to ensure they receive the high level of service they have come to expect with tfg key features risk managementrisk management is core to tfg’s asset management platform from independent valuation through live value at risk and stress testing to comprehensive reporting all supported by tfg’s knowledge of financial marketsfront officetfg offers a flexible portfolio management platform to support your business whatever your trading strategy is tfg completes live valuation risk measurement and market monitoring integrate seamlessly with third party systems our commitment to service lets you stay focused on the marketsmiddle office toolstfg knows what works for a middle office because tfg has run a middle office we know what best practice is we give you all of the tools you need to run your middle office as efficiently as possibleimplementationtfg systems is a customer led organisation who listens and reacts to the demands of our users throughout the cycle of ownership of tfg software from the first phone call enquiry to installation and trade entry there is a dedicated team who listen and react to your needs key benefits no information productservice